Esitatimendeni izolo iSACP, income isinqumo soMnyango wezokuHlunyeleliswa kweziMilo oholwa nguMnuz Ronald Lamola, sokungamdedeli umbulali kaHani. UHani wabulawa ngo-Ephreli 10, 1993. Umnyango kaLamola umemezele ukuthi isicelo sikaWalus sikashwele abasamukeli. “Ungqongqoshe wenze okufanele ngokuba angamnikezi umbulali ushwele. UWalus wayegwetshwe intambo, waya nakwiTruth and Reconciliation Commission efuna ukuxolelwa, okungenzekanga. Kulo nyaka kuphela iminyaka engu-27 uWalus abulala uHani kodwa namanje alikho iqiniso eliphelele ngokwenzeka,” kusho isitatimende seSACP. UHani wayeyilungu lesigungu esiphezulu se-ANC ngesikhathi ebulawa kanti wayeke wahola amasosha oMkhonto weSizwe ngaphambilini. Isibhamu esasetshenziswa uWalus kuthiwa sathathwa, akukaze kuvele ukuthi sathathwa ubani futhi wasiyisa kuphi? Ngokusho kwe-SACP, konke lokhu okungakaze kuchazwe kahle uWalus, ikhona kanye okumele anganikezwa ushwele ngenxa yakho. UWalus ugcinwe ejele iKgosi Mampuru II Centre ePitoli.